The unique identifier to a benefits plan, along with a string describing the benefits plan. Identifies the benefit plan or plans that can be used for Benefit Enrollment and Benefit Eligibility. Enrollment is checked when the benefit plan year falls within the effective date. Otherwise, if the benefit plan year falls outside of the effective data, then eligibility is checked.. Supports multiple values.
